DarkMouse::
She jumped down as the missles hit the base. "What in the slag? Who 
does this bot think he is?"

::KitKat::
She heard the missles hit the base. "SLAG!" She looked at 
Megatron. "We'll talk later." She ran out of the room and towards the 
entrance. "Autoguns, arm and fire on intruders."

The autoguns tried to get a fix on Bounty's possition.  They couldn't 
get a clear fix but fired on the abnormal signal. Aiming in his 
general vecinity.
